<div id="sales-and-promotions-sms-examples-and-ideas"></div>
<h2>Sales and promotions SMS examples</h2>
<p>Sales and <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/text-promotions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">promotional SMS messages</a> are a cornerstone of successful <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/sms-marketing-examples/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">text message marketing strategies</a>. When crafted well, these messages can create urgency, drive immediate action, and reward subscriber loyalty. These examples demonstrate effective ways to structure promotional offers, announce sales, and encourage quick purchasing decisions.</p>
<h3>Cuddle Clones&#8217; flash sale alert</h3>
<p>Surprise subscribers with a flash sale that leverages urgency to encourage purchases, like <a href="https://cuddleclones.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cuddle Clones</a> does with this two-day flash sale.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-cuddle-clones-flash-sale-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from cuddle clones for a flash sale" width="924" height="882" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89657" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-cuddle-clones-flash-sale-png.webp 924w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-cuddle-clones-flash-sale-480x458.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 924px, 100vw" /></p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f9e8.png" alt="üß®" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <strong>Running Google Ads and worried you&#8217;re wasting spend?</strong> Find out with a free, instant audit &gt;&gt; <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/google-adwords?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_PPC_AWGrader_AWGrader">Google Ads Performance Grader</a></p>
<h3>Bombas&#8217; punny sale announcement</h3>
<p>Show off your brand personality with a fun sale message. <a href="https://bombas.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bombas</a> uses clever wordplay on their new Fuzzy Socks to make the promotion memorable.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-bombas-promotion-png.webp" alt="bombas sms marketing example" width="602" height="178" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89658" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-bombas-promotion-png.webp 602w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-bombas-promotion-480x142.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 602px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>MeUndies&#8217; collection sale announcement</h3>
<p>Hold a collection-specific sale to encourage customers to buy specific products, like <a href="https://www.meundies.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MeUndies</a> does with this playful text to announce 50% off their loungewear collection.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-meundies-sale-png.webp" alt="text message marketing example from meundies" width="916" height="1034" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89659" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-meundies-sale-png.webp 916w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-meundies-sale-480x542.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 916px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Henn√©&#8217;s subscriber-exclusive sale announcement</h3>
<p>Make subscribers feel special by offering a special sale only they can access. <a href="https://henneorganics.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Henn√©</a>&#8216;s subscriber-only sale positions their SMS list as a VIP club with special perks.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-henne-promo-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example henne promo" width="608" height="302" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89660" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-henne-promo-png.webp 608w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-henne-promo-480x238.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 608px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Jack Rogers&#8217; friends and family sale reminder text</h3>
<p>Remind customers when your sale is about to end like <a href="https://www.jackrogersusa.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jack Rogers</a> does. The urgency-focused language and deal highlights motivate immediate shopping action.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jack-rogers-friends-and-family-sale-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example jack rogers friends and family sale" width="596" height="194" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89661" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jack-rogers-friends-and-family-sale-png.webp 596w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jack-rogers-friends-and-family-sale-480x156.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 596px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Holo Taco&#8217;s Black Friday sale announcement</h3>
<p>Consider a simple text for your next sale announcement that gets the point across quickly and prevents it from getting lost, like <a href="https://www.holotaco.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Holo Taco</a> does with this sitewide Black Friday sale text.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-holo-taco-black-friday-png.webp" alt="text message marketing example holo taco black friday" width="916" height="796" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89662" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-holo-taco-black-friday-png.webp 916w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-holo-taco-black-friday-480x417.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 916px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>No√©mie&#8217;s gift-with-purchase text</h3>
<p>Use a gift-with-purchase incentive to excite shoppers and encourage them to add more to their cart than they may have initially planned. <a href="https://www.hellonoemie.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">No√©mie</a> offers shoppers a free single earring for Singles Day on purchases that meet a minimum threshold.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-singles-day-earrings-deal-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example - singles day promotion text" width="576" height="304" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89663" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-singles-day-earrings-deal-png.webp 576w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-singles-day-earrings-deal-480x253.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 576px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Rare Beauty&#8217;s six days of deals</h3>
<p>Keep shoppers coming back for more with multiple days of deals‚Äîparticularly impactful near Black Friday/Cyber Monday and the winter gift-giving holidays when customers are already in buying mode. <a href="https://www.rarebeauty.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rare Beauty</a> builds anticipation for their Cyber Week event by teasing the daily deals to come.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-marketing-examples-rare-beauty-deals-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from rare beauty for cyber week" width="698" height="684" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89615" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-marketing-examples-rare-beauty-deals-png.webp 698w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-marketing-examples-rare-beauty-deals-480x470.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 698px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Buoy&#8217;s Black Friday early access text</h3>
<p>Give your SMS subscribers early access to your sales, like <a href="https://justaddbuoy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Buoy</a> does for Black Friday. This incentivizes customers to stay subscribed, and by encouraging early shopping, you stand out from the noise on <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/black-friday-marketing-ideas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Black Friday</a> itself.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-buoy-black-friday-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from buoy for black friday" width="580" height="302" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89664" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-buoy-black-friday-png.webp 580w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-buoy-black-friday-480x250.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 580px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Supergoop!&#8217;s early access sale reminder</h3>
<p>Remind your SMS subscribers that their early access is ending, like <a href="https://supergoop.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Supergoop!</a> does with their sitewide sale. This is especially effective if you have limited quantities, and customers might lose out on deals after the sale opens to the public.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-supergoop-early-access-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from supergoop" width="536" height="204" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89665" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-supergoop-early-access-png.webp 536w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-supergoop-early-access-480x183.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 536px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Haven Athletic&#8217;s presale announcement</h3>
<p>Turn stockouts into opportunities by offering customers the chance to preorder popular items. <a href="https://havenathletic.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Haven Athletic</a> builds excitement around their sold-out backpacks by highlighting their popularity and offering customers first access to the next batch.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-haven-athletic-presale-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from haven athletic" width="632" height="534" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89666" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-haven-athletic-presale-png.webp 632w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-haven-athletic-presale-480x406.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 632px, 100vw" /></p>
<div id="product-launch-and-update-text-message-examples"></div>
<h2>Product launch and update text message examples</h2>
<p>Help customers stay current with your offerings while creating excitement and urgency around shopping opportunities. Build anticipation for upcoming <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/04/20/go-to-market-strategy">product launches</a>, introduce new products, and let customers know if their products might go out of stock soon. Keep them informed about pricing changes to encourage them to buy when the price is low. And update them on new opportunities to shop in person.</p>
<h3>Half Magic Beauty&#8217;s customer-driven product announcement</h3>
<p>Show customers you&#8217;re listening by launching products or variants they&#8217;ve requested. <a href="https://halfmagicbeauty.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Half Magic Beauty</a> emphasizes that their new glitter shade is a result of customer feedback.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-half-magic-beauty-bestseller-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from half magic beauty about bestsellers" width="936" height="806" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89669" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-half-magic-beauty-bestseller-png.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-half-magic-beauty-bestseller-480x413.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f916.png" alt="ü§ñ" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <strong>AI can help you craft stand-out SMS marketing messages.</strong> Free download &gt;&gt; <a href="https://marketing.localiq.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsiteAIinMarketingGuide.html?cid=Web_Any_BlogInContent_PPC_AIMarketing_Download">Emergency Guide to AI in Marketing</a></p>
<h3>Little Sleepies&#8217; limited-edition launch announcement</h3>
<p>Launch limited-edition collections that tap into current moments and moods. <a href="https://littlesleepies.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Little Sleepies</a> creates excitement for their winter collection by using seasonal themes.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-little-sleepies-limited-edition-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from little sleepies for limited edition product" width="534" height="206" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89670" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-little-sleepies-limited-edition-png.webp 534w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-little-sleepies-limited-edition-480x185.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 534px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Armra&#8217;s new bundle announcement</h3>
<p>Encourage customers to try new products with bundle deals. <a href="https://tryarmra.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Armra</a> describes these two products as synergistic, encouraging them to try both.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-armra-bundle-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from armra about bundled products" width="918" height="922" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89671" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-armra-bundle-png.webp 918w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-armra-bundle-480x482.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 918px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Armra&#8217;s join-the-waitlist text</h3>
<p>Build anticipation for product launches and restocks by inviting customers to join the waitlist. Armra makes their waitlist message engaging with a fun tone and emphasizes scarcity to drive signups.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-armra-waitlist-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from armra about product waitlist" width="830" height="818" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89672" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-armra-waitlist-png.webp 830w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-armra-waitlist-480x473.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 830px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Marea&#8217;s restock alert</h3>
<p>Prioritize your VIPs by giving them first access to popular restocks. <a href="https://mareawellness.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marea</a> makes subscribers feel special by creating exclusivity around their restock. Bonus: For customers who receive replenishments automatically, Marea proactively offers customers the option to switch their recurring orders to this restocked product variant.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-restock-vips-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from marea about restocks" width="602" height="360" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89673" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-restock-vips-png.webp 602w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-restock-vips-480x287.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 602px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Kosas&#8217; restock reminder</h3>
<p>It&#8217;s helpful to remind subscribers about important announcements more than once‚Äîit&#8217;s easy for messages to get lost in the inbox! <a href="https://kosas.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kosas</a> shares a quick reminder text about their restock and emphasizes the Rosewater shade&#8217;s popularity and versatility to make it feel like a must-have summer essential.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-kosas-back-in-stock-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from kosas about restocks" width="578" height="234" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89674" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-kosas-back-in-stock-png.webp 578w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-kosas-back-in-stock-480x194.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 578px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Casely&#8217;s price drop notification</h3>
<p>Turn price drops into exciting news for interested customers. <a href="https://www.getcasely.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Casely</a> sends price drop messages to customers who have shown interest in the product, which could be what they need to buy.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-casely-price-drop-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from casely about price drops" width="472" height="978" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89675" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-casely-price-drop-png.webp 472w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-casely-price-drop-145x300.webp 145w" sizes="(max-width: 472px) 100vw, 472px" /></p>
