<h3>Pela&#8217;s price increase announcement</h3>
<p>On the flip side, if prices are going up, give customers a heads-up so they can stock up at the current price. <a href="https://pelacase.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pela</a> explains their reasoning transparently and softens the news with a bundle deal.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-pela-case-price-increase-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from pela about price increase" width="596" height="384" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89676" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-pela-case-price-increase-png.webp 596w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-pela-case-price-increase-480x309.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 596px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>You can learn <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/08/03/price-increase-letter-examples">how to write a price increase letter</a> here.</p>
<h3>Native&#8217;s retail partnership announcement</h3>
<p>Share retail expansion news with customers‚Äîespecially if you&#8217;ll be at a store near them. That way, they can still buy essentials from your brand if they run out before they remember to place an order online. <a href="https://www.nativecos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Native</a> announces their Costco availability while highlighting the value of buying in bulk.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-native-costco-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from native about costco partnership" width="492" height="336" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89677" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-native-costco-png.webp 492w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-native-costco-480x328.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 492px, 100vw" /></p>
<div id="product-recommendation-sms-examples"></div>
<h2>Product recommendation SMS examples</h2>
<p>Help customers find their perfect products through <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/04/22/how-to-personalize-ecommerce-customer-journey">personalized recommendations</a>, interactive quizzes, and curated guides. By matching customers with products that best suit their needs, these messages reduce decision fatigue and increase purchase confidence.</p>
<h3>Bombas&#8217; product recommendation quiz</h3>
<p>Help customers find the right products with a link to a <a href="https://www.convertflow.com/blog/product-recommendation-quiz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">product recommendation quiz</a>. In classic Bombas style, they use witty wordplay (&#8220;solemate&#8221;) to make an otherwise drab product (socks) feel fun.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-bombas-quiz-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from bombas with quiz link" width="572" height="178" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89678" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-bombas-quiz-png.webp 572w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-bombas-quiz-480x149.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 572px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Ami Col√©&#8217;s conversational product recommendation text</h3>
<p>You can also recommend products right in the text thread with a <a href="https://www.klaviyo.com/blog/conversational-sms">conversational SMS</a> flow like <a href="https://www.amicole.com/">Ami Col√©</a> does with this fun shade recommendation message.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-ami-cole-interactive-shopper-text-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from ami cole with interactive recommendations" width="1280" height="1510" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89679" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-ami-cole-interactive-shopper-text-png.webp 1280w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-ami-cole-interactive-shopper-text-980x1156.webp 980w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-ami-cole-interactive-shopper-text-480x566.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) 1280px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Kosas&#8217; TikTok filter product recommendation text</h3>
<p>You can also recommend the right products by using interactive social media tools like Kosas did with their custom TikTok filter. The filter lets you virtually try on Kosas&#8217; eyeliner to find what shades you like. Then Kosas directs them to a money-saving bundle offer.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-kosas-tiktok-filter-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from kosas with tiktok filter rec" width="616" height="276" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89680" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-kosas-tiktok-filter-png.webp 616w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-kosas-tiktok-filter-480x215.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 616px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Dan The Baking Man&#8217;s cart-building SMS flow</h3>
<p>Streamline subscribers&#8217; path to purchase by recommending products in the text thread, then send them a link with their cart to check out. <a href="https://danthebakingman.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dan The Baking Man</a> helps shoppers build their cart by asking what flavor cookies they want and how many, then sends them a link to check out complete with a discount. All they have to do is plug in their shipping and payment information.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-dan-the-baking-man-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from dan the baking man" width="1440" height="1376" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89681" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-dan-the-baking-man-png.webp 1440w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-dan-the-baking-man-1280x1223.webp 1280w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-dan-the-baking-man-980x936.webp 980w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-dan-the-baking-man-480x459.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) and (max-width: 1280px) 1280px, (min-width: 1281px) 1440px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>No√©mie book-a-consultation text</h3>
<p>Make high-value purchases more comfortable by offering personalized consultation options. No√©mie gives customers flexibility by providing in-person and virtual appointments to explore their jewelry, ask questions, and get expert advice from associates.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-appointment-booking-reminder-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from noemie with appointment booking reminder" width="598" height="306" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89683" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-appointment-booking-reminder-png.webp 598w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-appointment-booking-reminder-480x246.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 598px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Gladskin&#8217;s custom bundle-builder text</h3>
<p>Set bundles aren&#8217;t for everyone. If you have a lot of products that could mix and match, consider letting your customers build their own bundles. <a href="https://gladskin.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gladskin</a> makes its bundle offer appealing by emphasizing better savings the more customers buy.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-gladskin-build-bundle-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from gladskin to build bundle" width="940" height="1046" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89685" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-gladskin-build-bundle-png.webp 940w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-gladskin-build-bundle-480x534.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 940px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Fenty Beauty&#8217;s Mother&#8217;s Day gift guide text</h3>
<p>Help subscribers find the right products for their loved ones with curated shopping guides. <a href="https://fentybeauty.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fenty Beauty</a> leverages Rihanna&#8217;s star power to promote one product and shares their gift guide for more ideas.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-fenty-beauty-gift-guide-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from fenty with mothers day gift guide" width="600" height="294" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89686" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-fenty-beauty-gift-guide-png.webp 600w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-fenty-beauty-gift-guide-480x235.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 600px, 100vw" /></p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="üö®" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <strong>Get marketing, promotion, and social post ideas for every month of the year &gt;&gt;</strong> <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/resources/marketing-calendar?cid=Web_WS_InContent_Guide_2025MarketingCalendar_Download&amp;itm_source=wordstream&amp;itm_medium=blog&amp;itm_campaign=incontent_links">The Mega Must-Have Marketing Calendar</a></p>
<div id="welcome-text-message-ideas-and-examples"></div>
<h2>Welcome text message examples</h2>
<p>Make a strong first impression with new subscribers through thoughtfully crafted welcome messages. These initial texts set the tone for your SMS relationship while incentivizing first purchases through special offers.</p>
<h3>Vuori&#8217;s welcome text</h3>
<p>Make new subscribers feel welcome with a friendly introduction message. <a href="https://vuoriclothing.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vuori</a> sets the tone for their SMS relationship by warmly welcoming new subscribers while highlighting what their brand is all about.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-vouri-welecome-text-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from vuori with welcome text" width="432" height="552" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89687" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-vouri-welecome-text-png.webp 432w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-vouri-welecome-text-235x300.webp 235w" sizes="(max-width: 432px) 100vw, 432px" /></p>
<h3>GhostBed&#8217;s limited-time offer welcome text</h3>
<p>Motivate quick first purchases with a time-sensitive welcome offer. <a href="https://www.ghostbed.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GhostBed</a>&#8216;s limited-time welcome discount creates urgency for new subscribers.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-ghostbed-sale-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from ghostbed about limited time offer sale" width="928" height="672" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89688" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-ghostbed-sale-png.webp 928w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-ghostbed-sale-480x348.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 928px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Jack Rogers&#8217; welcome discount expiration reminders</h3>
<p>If your welcome incentive expires, drive conversions by reminding new subscribers before they miss out. Jack Rogers increases the effectiveness of their <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2017/08/18/welcome-email">welcome promotion</a> by sending well-timed reminders leading up to the deadline.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jack-rogers-welcome-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from jack rogers with welcome promo" width="684" height="574" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89689" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jack-rogers-welcome-png.webp 684w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jack-rogers-welcome-480x403.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 684px, 100vw" /></p>
<div id="customer-engagement-sms-ideas"></div>
<h2>Customer engagement SMS examples</h2>
<p>Build stronger connections with your audience through interactive and entertaining SMS content. These messages go beyond pure promotion to create two-way conversations, gather feedback, and make customers feel like valued community members.</p>
<h3>Graza&#8217;s guess-the-product text</h3>
<p>Tease a new product by cloaking it in a mystery. Graza uses conversational text messaging to get subscribers to guess their next product launch.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-graza-new-product-announcement-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from graza about new product announcement" width="940" height="882" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89690" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-graza-new-product-announcement-png.webp 940w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-graza-new-product-announcement-480x450.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 940px, 100vw" /></p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f4da.png" alt="üìö" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />¬†<strong>Free guide download</strong>¬†&gt;&gt;¬†<a href="https://marketing.wordstream.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsite36CallToActionPhrases.html?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_36CallToActionPhrases_Download">The 42 Best Call to Action Phrases Ever (&amp; Why They Work)</a></p>
<h3>Cocofloss&#8217;s proactive customer support text</h3>
<p>Shoppers may linger on questions without asking, ultimately delaying their purchase. Take a page from <a href="https://cocofloss.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cocofloss</a>&#8216;s book and offer support proactively. Cocofloss makes their support message welcoming by introducing a named concierge who can help.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-cocofloss-personal-shopper-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from cocofloss with product recommendations" width="582" height="166" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89691" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-cocofloss-personal-shopper-png.webp 582w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-cocofloss-personal-shopper-480x137.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 582px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Blenders&#8217; giveaway announcement</h3>
<p>Drive engagement with an enticing giveaway contest. <a href="https://www.blenderseyewear.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Blenders</a> lets shoppers enter for free, but they increase their chances of winning by placing an order. This encourages engagement and sales.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-blenders-contest-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from blenders about contest" width="642" height="502" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89692" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-blenders-contest-png.webp 642w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-blenders-contest-480x375.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 642px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>L&#8217;AMARUE&#8217;s call for customer stories</h3>
<p>Collect testimonials you can repurpose across your marketing channels by inviting customers to share their success stories. <a href="https://www.shoplamarue.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">L&#8217;AMARUE</a> makes their request personal with a signoff from their cofounders.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-community-stories-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from l'amarue looking for customer stories" width="618" height="456" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89693" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-community-stories-png.webp 618w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-community-stories-480x354.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 618px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Stratia&#8217;s community-building text message</h3>
<p>More loyalty can be forged when customers have a chance to connect with like-minded brand enthusiasts. So <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/12/19/brand-community">start a community</a> where they can connect with each other‚Äîlike on Facebook or Discord. Stratia builds their brand community by inviting customers to join a Discord server for skincare discussions and tips.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-stratia-community-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from stratia about online community" width="486" height="234" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89694" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-stratia-community-png.webp 486w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-stratia-community-480x231.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 486px, 100vw" /></p>
<div id="social-proof-sms-marketing-examples-and-ideas"></div>
<h2>Social proof SMS marketing ideas and examples</h2>
<p>Leverage the power of <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2017/07/19/customer-testimonial-examples">customer testimonials</a>, influencer partnerships, and user-generated content in your SMS marketing. <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/social-proof-examples/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Social proof</a> messages build trust and credibility by showing real people enjoying and benefiting from your products.</p>
<h3>Caraway&#8217;s customer review text message</h3>
<p>Share a customer review that addresses common product concerns. <a href="https://www.carawayhome.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Caraway</a> highlights a glowing review that speaks directly to the ease of use of their cast iron.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-caraway-testimonial-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from caraway with customer testimonial" width="610" height="368" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89695" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-caraway-testimonial-png.webp 610w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-caraway-testimonial-480x290.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 610px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>WeWoreWhat&#8217;s UGC text</h3>
<p>Celebrate your customers by highlighting how they use your products with <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2014/04/28/user-generated-content">user-generated content (UGC)</a>. WeWoreWhat compliments their community while encouraging others to shop featured styles.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-weworewhat-ugc-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from weworewhat with user generated content" width="464" height="966" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89696" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-weworewhat-ugc-png.webp 464w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-weworewhat-ugc-144x300.webp 144w" sizes="(max-width: 464px) 100vw, 464px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>Poppi&#8217;s influencer social proof text</h3>
<p>Leverage influencer and celebrity features to create excitement and drive sales. Poppi turns a natural product placement in Hailey Bieber&#8217;s video into a timely promotion with an on-theme discount code. Even if you don&#8217;t get a big celebrity featuring your products, smaller influencers that your audience will know can provide a boost.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-poppi-influencer-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from poppi with influencer partnership" width="454" height="966" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89697" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-poppi-influencer-png.webp 454w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-poppi-influencer-141x300.webp 141w" sizes="(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<div id="abandonment-text-message-ideas"></div>
<h2>Abandonment text message ideas</h2>
<p>Recover potentially lost sales by reconnecting with customers who have shown interest but haven&#8217;t completed their purchase. These text messages can provide that gentle reminder or extra incentive needed to turn browsers into buyers.</p>
<h3>Our Place&#8217;s browse abandonment text</h3>
<p>Re-engage browsers by mentioning specific products they viewed. <a href="https://fromourplace.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Our Place</a> creates urgency for its Always Pan by mentioning its tendency to sell out quickly.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-our-place-come-back-png.webp" alt="sms marketing come back example from our place" width="904" height="768" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89698" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-our-place-come-back-png.webp 904w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-our-place-come-back-480x408.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 904px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>INH Hair&#8217;s low-stock abandoned cart alert</h3>
<p>If stock is running low, you can leverage that to create even more urgency around browsing and cart abandonment text messages. <a href="https://inhhair.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">INH Hair</a> sends a simple, direct message encouraging shoppers to complete their order before what&#8217;s in their cart goes out of stock.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-low-stock-reminder-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example low stock reminder" width="536" height="124" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89700" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-low-stock-reminder-png.webp 536w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-low-stock-reminder-480x111.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 536px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Beachwaver&#8217;s holiday sale abandoned cart reminder</h3>
<p>Another great way to get customers to finalize their purchase is to highlight new savings that have become available thanks to a sale. Beachwaver updates their abandoned cart flows during sales to tell shoppers they can save on the items in their cart.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-beachwaver-memorial-day-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from beachwaver" width="512" height="1070" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89701" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-beachwaver-memorial-day-png.webp 512w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-beachwaver-memorial-day-480x1003.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 512px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love?filters=triggered" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<div id="loyalty-and-retention-sms-marketing-ideas-with-examples"></div>
<h2>Loyalty and retention SMS marketing ideas with examples</h2>
<p>Keep your existing customers engaged and coming back for more with messages that <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-run-customer-loyalty-programs/">reward loyalty</a>, encourage referrals, and gather feedback. These texts help strengthen customer relationships and increase lifetime value through thoughtful engagement strategies.</p>
<h3>Marleylilly&#8217;s rewards program invitation</h3>
<p>Keep shoppers coming back by inviting them to join your rewards program. <a href="https://marleylilly.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marleylilly</a> thanks subscribers for their initial purchase and lets them know they can earn points and get perks on future purchases.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-marleylilly-cyber-week-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from marleylilly about rewards program" width="484" height="1006" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89702" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-marleylilly-cyber-week-png.webp 484w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-marleylilly-cyber-week-480x998.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 484px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love?filters=triggered" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>Swap&#8217;s refer-a-friend invitation</h3>
<p>After a shopper&#8217;s purchase, consider rewarding them for referring a friend. That spreads the word about your brand while encouraging repeat purchases. <a href="https://swap.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Swap</a> gives their customers a whopping 40% off when a customer&#8217;s referral makes a purchase.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-swap-share-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from swap about refer a friend program" width="466" height="974" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89704" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-swap-share-png.webp 466w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-swap-share-144x300.webp 144w" sizes="(max-width: 466px) 100vw, 466px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love?filters=post-purchase" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>Flux&#8217;s cashback offer text</h3>
<p>Cashback offers are becoming a preferred welcome incentive for many brands over first-purchase discounts. While shoppers can get the cash on a Visa card, many brands give a bonus when customers opt for store credit instead, so it inherently <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/03/09/customer-retention-strategies">encourages retention</a>. Flux offers subscribers 20% cash back as a welcome incentive.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-flux-footwear-join-community-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from flux footwear about customer incentive program" width="924" height="944" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89706" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-flux-footwear-join-community-png.webp 924w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-flux-footwear-join-community-480x490.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 924px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Native&#8217;s subscription upsell text message</h3>
<p>Subscribe-and-save offers can help customers get more of the products they love on a consistent basis. Native texts customers after their purchase to upsell them to recurring orders so they never run out.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-native-subscription-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from native about subscription program" width="498" height="422" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89707" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-native-subscription-png.webp 498w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-native-subscription-480x407.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 498px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Whirley Pop Shop&#8217;s invitation for replenishment reminders</h3>
<p>An alternative to getting customers to subscribe to recurring orders is reminding them to reorder before they run out. Whirley Pop Shop lets customers opt into reminders at a frequency that works for them.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-whirleypopshop-purchase-reminder-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from whirleypop" width="472" height="976" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89708" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-whirleypopshop-purchase-reminder-png.webp 472w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-whirleypopshop-purchase-reminder-145x300.webp 145w" sizes="(max-width: 472px) 100vw, 472px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love?filters=post-purchase" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>Skull Shaver&#8217;s text-to-buy replenishment reminder</h3>
<p>Make it even easier for customers to purchase again with a text-to-order automation. <a href="https://skullshaver.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Skull Shaver</a> lets subscribers place a new order by simply replying with a keyword.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-skull-shaver-sale-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from skull shaver" width="452" height="756" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89710" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-skull-shaver-sale-png.webp 452w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-skull-shaver-sale-179x300.webp 179w" sizes="(max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/blog/text-to-buy-strategies" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>No√©mie&#8217;s customer survey text</h3>
<p>Make customers feel valued by asking for feedback. No√©mie sent a <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2014/11/10/best-online-survey-tools">quick survey</a> to subscribers and paired it with a sweet discount.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-survey-request-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from noemie about survey" width="572" height="310" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89711" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-survey-request-png.webp 572w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-survey-request-480x260.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 572px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Stratia&#8217;s winback text message</h3>
<p>When customers haven&#8217;t purchased in a while, send a quick note to remind them what they&#8217;re missing. Stratia offers a coupon to dormant subscribers.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-stratia-come-back-text-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from stratia to come back" width="488" height="244" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89712" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-stratia-come-back-text-png.webp 488w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-stratia-come-back-text-480x240.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 488px, 100vw" /></p>
<div id="educational-sms-marketing-ideas-with-examples"></div>
<h2>Educational SMS marketing ideas</h2>
<p>Add value to your SMS marketing by teaching customers about your products, sharing useful tips, and providing helpful resources. These messages help customers get the most out of their purchases while positioning your brand as a trusted authority.</p>
<h3>L&#8217;AMARUE&#8217;s core ingredient education text</h3>
<p>If your product or the materials it&#8217;s made of are unusual, you could incorporate product education into your SMS marketing plan like L&#8217;AMARUE does with its proprietary ingredient. Since they&#8217;ve trademarked this ingredient, customers won&#8217;t see it anywhere else. So explaining its benefits is essential for getting them to understand its value.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-new-product-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from l'amarue about ingredients in new product" width="946" height="1114" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89713" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-new-product-png.webp 946w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-new-product-480x565.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 946px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Girlfriend Collective&#8217;s fabric education text</h3>
<p>If you sell primarily online, product education can help customers understand your products without seeing them in person. <a href="https://girlfriend.com/">Girlfriend Collective</a> is another brand that uses product education in its SMS marketing campaigns. These descriptions help customers get a feel for the fabric, which can&#8217;t be conveyed in product photos.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jerseylounge-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from girlfriend collective" width="586" height="204" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89714" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jerseylounge-png.webp 586w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jerseylounge-480x167.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 586px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Lively&#8217;s product care text message</h3>
<p>Your job isn&#8217;t done when a customer buys your product. Helping them use it effectively through care tips helps them extend the life of their product, which makes them more likely to love it and come back for more. That&#8217;s why Lively shares product care tips in a post-purchase SMS flow.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lively-hacks-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from lively" width="466" height="972" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89715" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lively-hacks-png.webp 466w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lively-hacks-144x300.webp 144w" sizes="(max-width: 466px) 100vw, 466px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love?filters=post-purchase" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>Kosas&#8217; product tutorial text</h3>
<p>You can also help customers get more out of their products by showing them how to use them. As part of one product launch, Kosas shows customers how to use their new brightening powder. Beyond providing helpful instructions, this showcases the product&#8217;s benefits, therefore increasing purchases.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-kosas-how-to-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from kosas with how to" width="924" height="882" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89716" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-kosas-how-to-png.webp 924w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-kosas-how-to-480x458.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 924px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>L&#8217;AMARUE&#8217;s FAQ answers</h3>
<p>Proactively answer common customer questions to help them get the most out of their products and address objections to purchase. L&#8217;AMARUE answers a common skincare question in this SMS campaign.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-faqs-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example of faq from lamarue" width="922" height="1072" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89617" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-faqs-png.webp 922w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-faqs-480x558.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 922px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Graza&#8217;s recipe text</h3>
<p>Provide valuable content that helps customers use your products creatively. Graza shares a seasonal pie recipe from a respected baker inspires customers.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-graza-recipe-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from graza of recipe" width="656" height="1006" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89618" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-graza-recipe-png.webp 656w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-graza-recipe-480x736.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 656px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Stratia&#8217;s educational blog share</h3>
<p>If your brand has a blog, share new posts with your SMS subscribers to provide value to your audience while getting more out of that content. Stratia shared a blog post about the science behind hydrated skin soon after launching their hydrating toner. So it benefited their sales for that launch, too.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-stratia-blog-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example promoting new blog post" width="490" height="136" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89619" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-stratia-blog-png.webp 490w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-stratia-blog-480x133.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 490px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>MATE the Label&#8217;s sustainability report</h3>
<p>If your brand has any social or environmental initiatives, share your progress transparently to build trust and brand affinity. <a href="https://matethelabel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MATE the Label</a> shares their sustainability impact over the past year and their plans for the future.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-mate-impact-report-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example of impact report from mate the label" width="462" height="970" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89620" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-mate-impact-report-png.webp 462w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-mate-impact-report-143x300.webp 143w" sizes="(max-width: 462px) 100vw, 462px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love?filters=social-impact" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<div id="seasonal-and-timely-sms-marketing-ideas"></div>
<h2>Seasonal and timely SMS marketing ideas</h2>
<p>Connect with customers throughout the year with messages that align with seasons, holidays, and cultural moments. These timely texts help your brand stay relevant while creating natural opportunities for engagement and promotion.</p>
<h3>L&#8217;AMARUE&#8217;s healthy habits series</h3>
<p>Boost engagement with an ongoing series of valuable tips and advice. L&#8217;AMARUE helps customers kick off the New Year on the right foot with daily healthy habits tips. Before starting the series, they asked customers if they wanted to opt in, which ensured only the customers who wanted to receive daily texts did.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-tip-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example of healthy tips from beauty brand" width="612" height="368" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89621" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-tip-png.webp 612w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-lamarue-tip-480x289.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 612px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Uncommon Goods&#8217; campaign opt-out text</h3>
<p>On the flip side, you can also give subscribers the option to opt <em>out</em> of text message campaigns for a period of time. Uncommon Goods knows how difficult certain holidays can be for customers, so they give them the option to pause campaigns.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-uncommon-goods-fathers-day-png.webp" alt="example of sms marketing opt out text for fathers day" width="508" height="1064" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89622" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-uncommon-goods-fathers-day-png.webp 508w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-uncommon-goods-fathers-day-480x1005.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 508px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love?filters=conversational" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>Ami Col√©&#8217;s cultural moment text</h3>
<p>Jump on the excitement of what&#8217;s happening in your subscribers&#8217; greater cultural context, for example, a popular movie release or a big sports event. Ami Col√© celebrates the Emmys with a product recommendation that matches the vibes of the awards event.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-emmys-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example - emmys related text" width="828" height="232" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89623" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-emmys-png.webp 828w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-emmys-480x134.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 828px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Half Magic Beauty&#8217;s Halloween shipping deadline notice</h3>
<p>Help customers get products in time for specific events, like Christmas gift giving, by clearly communicating holiday shipping deadlines. Half Magic Beauty ensures customers get their Halloween makeup on time by sending a timely reminder about ordering cutoffs.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-half-magic-beauty-halloween-png.webp" alt="example of text marketing message for halloween" width="582" height="194" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89624" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-half-magic-beauty-halloween-png.webp 582w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-half-magic-beauty-halloween-480x160.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 582px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Saatchi Art&#8217;s last-minute gift card text</h3>
<p>For customers that miss a shipping deadline, offer gift cards as a solution for last-minute shopping. Saatchi Art saves the day by promoting digital gift cards.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-saatchi-art-last-minute-gift-png.webp" alt="sms example gift card promo" width="468" height="970" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89625" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-saatchi-art-last-minute-gift-png.webp 468w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-saatchi-art-last-minute-gift-145x300.webp 145w" sizes="(max-width: 468px) 100vw, 468px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love?filters=gift-cards" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>Luna Grill honors the military on Veterans&#8217; Day</h3>
<p>Show appreciation for different communities by offering special promotions. For example, you could honor teachers during back-to-school or first responders on National First Responders Day. <a href="https://lunagrill.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Luna Grill</a> supports military members with a Veterans&#8217; Day offer for a free entr√©e.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-luna-grill-military-discount-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example for veterans day" width="598" height="396" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89626" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-luna-grill-military-discount-png.webp 598w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-luna-grill-military-discount-480x318.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 598px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>The Sill&#8217;s niche holiday text message</h3>
<p>Leverage lesser-known holidays to create relevant promotional opportunities. <a href="https://www.thesill.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Sill</a> turns National Pet Day into a smart marketing moment by highlighting their pet-safe plant collection.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-the-sill-national-pet-day-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example for national pet day" width="928" height="828" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89627" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-the-sill-national-pet-day-png.webp 928w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-the-sill-national-pet-day-480x428.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 928px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Jack Rogers&#8217; treat-yourself holiday text</h3>
<p>Turn traditional gift-giving holidays into self-care opportunities. Jack Rogers encourages mothers to treat themselves with a special discount.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jack-rogers-mothers-day-png.webp" alt="jack rogers mothers day text marketing example" width="614" height="244" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89628" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jack-rogers-mothers-day-png.webp 614w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-jack-rogers-mothers-day-480x191.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 614px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Monos&#8217; holiday gift guide text</h3>
<p>Make holiday shopping easier with curated <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-create-a-holiday-gift-guide/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gift guides</a> for different audiences. Monos helps customers find the perfect travel gear gifts while reducing decision fatigue during the busy holiday season.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-monos-gift-guide-png.webp" alt="sms marketing gift guide example" width="640" height="582" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89629" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-monos-gift-guide-png.webp 640w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-monos-gift-guide-480x437.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 640px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Graza&#8217;s seasonal playlist</h3>
<p>Build brand affinity by sharing lifestyle content that goes beyond product promotion. Graza strengthens their connection with customers by curating a seasonal playlist.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-graza-song-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example of playlist from graza" width="648" height="689" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89630" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-graza-song-png.webp 648w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-graza-song-480x510.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 648px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Every Man Jack&#8217;s Giving Tuesday text</h3>
<p>Connect with customers through charitable initiatives sparked by the calendar. Every Man Jack shows their brand values by participating in Giving Tuesday with a meaningful philanthropic campaign.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-every-man-jack-giving-tuesday-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from every man jack for giving tuesday" width="462" height="970" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89718" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-every-man-jack-giving-tuesday-png.webp 462w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-every-man-jack-giving-tuesday-143x300.webp 143w" sizes="(max-width: 462px) 100vw, 462px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.attentive.com/texts-we-love?filters=social-impact" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<h3>Flux&#8217;s gratitude text</h3>
<p>Build customer relationships by sharing messages of appreciation during the fall season. Flux strengthens customer loyalty by expressing gratitude to their community.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-flux-footwear-thanksgiving-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from flux footwear for thanksgiving" width="916" height="900" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89719" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-flux-footwear-thanksgiving-png.webp 916w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-flux-footwear-thanksgiving-480x472.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 916px, 100vw" /></p>
<div id="transactional-sms-marketing-ideas-and-examples"></div>
<h2>Transactional SMS marketing ideas and examples</h2>
<p>Clear, helpful transactional messages keep customers informed about their purchases and appointments. These essential communications build trust and reduce support inquiries by proactively providing important updates and confirmations.</p>
<h3>Native&#8217;s order confirmation text</h3>
<p>Confirm that a customer&#8217;s order went through so they know everything is running smoothly. Native adds a tone of celebration and gratitude to their <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/07/07/thank-you-for-your-order-messages">order confirmation messages</a>.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-native-social-proof-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from native about order confirmation" width="584" height="392" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89721" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-native-social-proof-png.webp 584w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-native-social-proof-480x322.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 584px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Vessi&#8217;s order shipment confirmation</h3>
<p>Keep customers informed about their order status with clear shipping updates. <a href="https://vessi.com/">Vessi</a> maintains excitement for incoming purchases by promptly notifying customers when their orders ship.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-order-tracking-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from vessi about order tracking" width="602" height="296" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89720" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-order-tracking-png.webp 602w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-order-tracking-480x236.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 602px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Best Buy&#8217;s appointment confirmation text</h3>
<p>Make service appointment details clear with confirmation messages. Best Buy reminds customers of their appointment details and gives a link to reschedule if necessary.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-best-buy-appointment-reminder-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from best buy about appointment" width="594" height="164" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89722" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-best-buy-appointment-reminder-png.webp 594w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-best-buy-appointment-reminder-480x133.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 594px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Hustead&#8217;s Auto Body appointment reminder text</h3>
<p>Reduce no-shows with timely appointment reminders. <a href="https://husteads.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hustead&#8217;s Auto Body</a> helps customers keep their appointments by sending clear reminder messages.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-auto-shop-inspection-reminder-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from auto shop about inspection" width="608" height="456" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89723" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-auto-shop-inspection-reminder-png.webp 608w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-auto-shop-inspection-reminder-480x360.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 608px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3>Buoy&#8217;s delivery confirmation text</h3>
<p>Complete the purchase experience with friendly delivery notifications. Buoy ensures customers know when their orders have arrived safely at their destination‚Äîparticularly helpful to avoid packages getting stolen or damaged by the weather.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-buoy-order-arrival-png.webp" alt="sms marketing example from buoy about order arrival" width="594" height="264" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-89724" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-buoy-order-arrival-png.webp 594w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sms-example-buoy-order-arrival-480x213.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 594px, 100vw" /></p>
<h2>Upgrade your SMS marketing campaigns with fresh ideas and examples</h2>
<p>These SMS marketing ideas and examples span the practical to the inspired. Start adding the ideas that resonate most with your business goals to your SMS marketing strategy and see how your audience responds. Test different approaches and keep iterating based on the data.</p>
<p>Keep in mind that some of the most successful SMS marketing campaigns might start with inspiration from other brands, but they&#8217;ll evolve into something unique to your business. The brands that stand out are those that continuously experiment while staying true to their values and brand identity.</p>
<p>So take risks and experiment! The next best SMS marketing tactics are yet to be discovered.</p>
