		<title>17 Small Business Saturday Marketing Ideas Any Business Can Try</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/small-business-saturday-marketing</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Amanda Rodhe]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 17:45:53 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Marketing Ideas]]></category>
